  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Start_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  characterName: Ryan
  lines:
  - Shhhh! You must be new here..
  - Outside our camp there's one animal that's different from the rest. We've tried
    many times to approach it and gather intelligence on whether it is a threat or
    not.
  - Unfortunately we've had no success. Maybe you can give it a try for us? I'll
    reward you with some information when you succeed.
